local lang = RSRG.Languages["en"]
--The character is supposed to be and advanced tutorial that leads new players to key spots around the world space while also teaching them the purpose of key items and what they can be used for. Such as Advanced Materials, Ballistic Polymer, and Tech Data etc etc.

-- Mission Giver
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN"] = "Trail Warden Mei-Lian"
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_SUBTITLE"] = "Crimson Caravan"
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_NEW"] = "Nihao, you seem new around here talk to Isaac or Major Redmen for some odd jobs if you want something to do."
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_GREET_NO"] = "Piss off Gweilo, You have fucked over my friends too much."
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_GREET_0"] = "Daoqian, I have no work for you. come back when you prove you're competent to Issac and Major Redmen. I'll guide you from there."
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_GREET_150"] = "Outlander, you have proven that you can fight and be resourceful. I will help teach you how one survives in this hellscape."
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_GREET_300"] = "You have learned much Xuesheng, but there is still more you can be taught."
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_GREET_400"] = "$playername, you have proven to me that you are smarter than your average outlander. You might even be worthy of entering Jiayuan"
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_GREET_750"] = "$playername, you have returned good. Have you finished all the trials I have assigned to you?"
lang["#MISSION_GIVER_MEILIAN_GREET_999"] = "Nihao $playername, it is good to see you alive and well Banlu. You have done things I've seen few outlanders do. If you ever wish to travel south I think it would be nice for us to see my home."

-- Wild Wasteland (This quest line can be added to later on when we add more locations like Cutler City and Reno)
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND"] = "A Wild Wasteland"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND_DESC"] = "Well done, Outlander. You've shown Issac that you have the strength to survive. Now, let us prepare you for the path ahead. First, gather the necessary gear to travel through the northern climates by talking to Major Redmen and return to me when you are ready."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND_HINT"] = "Collect items fit for traveling north to mountain pass by completeing Redmen's quest and report back to Mei-Lian."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND_COMPLETE"] = "You again, what bring you back over to me? You need some gear for a caravan route. Fine here I owe her a favor anyway."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND1"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 2"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND1_DESC"] = "You're back, and you dont look like a homeless junkie anymore very good. Alright lets set out on the path towards mountain pass, once we get there I'll reconvene with you. See you then Outlander. "
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND1_HINT"] = "Travel to mountain pass and meet up with Mei Lian "
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND1_COMPLETE"] = "Give me a moment to direct where the injured guards need to get treated while we unload. Then I'll talk about what you can do next."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND2"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 3"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND2_DESC"] = "We have finally arrived—excellent work, Outlander. Given the ambush, I am surprised we lost only three guards. It could have been much worse. Now that we are in a safer place, it is time to rest and recuperate at Camp Willow. Take this opportunity to relax and regain your strength. Once you are refreshed, speak with the locals and learn about the land here. We will remain for some time, so it is essential to understand the area and its people before we proceed. Stay vigilant and prepared, as always."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND2_HINT"] = "Talk to Susan and complete some quests around mountain pass and explore the local area then return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND2_COMPLETE"] = "You just arrived in with the Crimson caravan group right? Good it means your competent I have work for you."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND2_CUSTOMUI"] =  "Talk to Susan and Complete some tasks"

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND3"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 3"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND3_DESC"] = "It seems you've made quite the impression on Susan. She was quite vocal about you being sent from the heavens with how much you helped her. Moving on to other more important matters, most of the other members of the caravan are just about ready to set out back on the High Road. Our next stop is going to be the Ashlands Region we should be able to rest at the city outpost camp that the locals have setup. I want you to scout ahead of us and I'll see you at city outpost when we arrive."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND3_HINT"] = "Travel to Ashland City Outpost region entrance and speak to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND3_COMPLETE"] = "Hey, give me a moment to direct where the goods need to be dropped then we can talk." 

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND4"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 4"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND4_DESC"] = "Welcome to the burnt out hell hole that is the Ashlands. There isnt much around here besides destroyed buildings wrecked cars and lots of Remnant Super Mutants from back when the master was around. Talk to Xanthan he's a local representative for the Cascade Caravan. He should have some work for you while we unload some cargo that they requested and after you talk to him go explore a little."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND4_HINT"] = "Talk to Xanthan and complete some quests for him also complete the exploration quests for Ashlands then return to Mei Lian. (It's also recommend you take as many quests as you can he is a good source of CXP and UXP. Also Ambomination is the only required quest from him) " 
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND4_COMPLETE"] = "You with the caravan that just came in? Interesting If you want I got some chalenges for you."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND4_CUSTOMUI"] =  "Talk to Xanthan and Complete tasks"

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND5"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 5"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND5_DESC"] = "Chūsè de, you return with perfect timing. All right lets get back on the Highroad to the north the next stop should be a location called Dead Estuary. We will be taking boats to a makeshift flotilla on a swamp. Same thing as before you're on scouting duty. Go ahead of us and look for any threats, I'll meet you at the flotilla."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND5_HINT"] = "Travel north to Dead Estuary and meet up with Mei Lian the Makeshift Flotilla region extrance."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND5_COMPLETE"] = "Nihao, give me a moment to direct where the sick caravan hands can get their radiation levels checked. Then I'll talk to you." 

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND6"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 6"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND6_DESC"] = "Careful Outlander, watch were you step the water in this region is flooded with radioactive pollutants. Keep out of it unless you have good protection against radiation because if you dont you're going to be stuck here for weeks fighting off a severe case of radiation poisoning. For now go talk to that scientist who's treating our sick and see if he needs help. Also I have a few locations around this region I need yout to survey while you're at it."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND6_HINT"] = "Talk to Melvin and complete some tasks for him then return to Mei-Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND6_COMPLETE"] = "You came in with that carvan group? While they checked for rads can you do some odd jobs for me?"
    lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND6_CUSTOMUI"] =  "Talk to Melvin"

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND7"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 7"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND7_DESC"] = "You're finally back good. The boats just got loaded with all the cargo we need lets get on the water and get back to the mainland. After that we're going to Oregon to a town called Salem. You know the drill by this point take a boat ahead of us and scout ahead, radio back if you see anything bad. Beyond that I'll see you at the Survivors Camp."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND7_HINT"] = "Travel to Salem and meet up with Mei Lian at the Survivors Camp"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND7_COMPLETE"] = "Zuìhòu, we an rest. Alright Banlu give me a moment to convene with the caravan then we can talk."

--You're finally back good. The boats just got loaded with all the cargo we need lets get on the water and get back to the mainland. After that we're going to Oregon to a town called Salem

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND8"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 8"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND8_DESC"] = "Alright friend, welcome to one of the last stops on our route. This place is called Salem it used to be a budding community before the mutant and Shadowed started to call this place home. Now it's just another bombed out hell hole with your generic assortment of things wanting to kill you. We have quite a few thing to unload for the local refugee population so go talk to Maverick and get some work done. Also I have a few places that need to be scouted around the city so talk to me if you want to help with that."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND8_HINT"] = "Go talk to Maverick and complete some quests for him and do some scouting work for Mei-lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND8_COMPLETE"] = "Who the fuck are you? Oh, your with that caravan that came in, well then I got work for you to earn your keep."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND8_CUSTOMUI"] =  "Talk to Maverick"

-- Well you've proven yourself beyond anything I though possible of an outlander. This was our last stop for this route so you're free to go your contract is completed

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND9"] = "A Wild Wasteland Part 9"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND9_DESC"] = "Well you've proven yourself beyond anything I though possible of an outlander. This was our last stop for this route so you're free to go your contract is completed. The only other thing I have you could possibly do is go kill a couple rejected mutants to make the area safer. Then return to me I'll have your contracts final payment ready "
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND9_HINT"] = "Go kill 5 Super Mutant Rejects and return to Mei-Lian to finish your contract"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_WILDWASTELAND9_COMPLETE"] = "Welcome back Banlu, with that task being done here is your payment. Check with me again sometime for more work."

--Mountain Pass unused at the moment but if points of interest are ever added we could use this quest giver for it

