lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_PRICESURVIVAL"] = "The Price of Survival"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_PRICESURVIVAL_DESC"] = "Their is a group operating out of this region called Cascade Caravan they would usually be competition for us but we've come to an arrangement. They operate a store in this region you should go take a look at what they sell they usually have some good stock. Once you check it out come back here and we'll see what you got."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_PRICESURVIVAL_HINT"] = "Go to the Vendor located on Ashlands to the right outside the Car tunnel region exit then return to Mei-Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_PRICESURVIVAL_COMPLETE"] = "Welcome back, lets take a look at what you bought if anything at all."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_GRITGUNPOWDER"] = "Grit and Gunpowder"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_GRITGUNPOWDER_DESC"] = "I have another location I need you to go survey. I've heard some talk from around the local camp about an old mine being somewhere in this region look for it and map its layout then return to me. I'll pay you for the the information"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_GRITGUNPOWDER_HINT"] = "Go to the Lead and Gunpowder Mine located in Ashlands straight outside the Car tunnel region exit below the Auto Body Shop then return to Mei-Lian."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_GRITGUNPOWDER_COMPLETE"] = "You mapped the location? Good, here is your payment for your efforts also try gathering some gunpowder from the mine sometime."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_FORSAKENREJECTS"] = "The Forsaken and Rejected"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_FORSAKENREJECTS_DESC"] = "Alright, I need have a scouting mission for you. This region is crawling with super mutants and they seem to congregate around an old town to the North east of here. Go to that location scout the gas station and get to the bottom of what their doing in there."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_FORSAKENREJECTS_HINT"] = "Go to the Old World town to the far right corner of the Ashlands region from City Outpost and delve into the depths of the Pre-war bunker complex and make it to the end then return to Mei-Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_FORSAKENREJECTS_COMPLETE"] = "You return, what did you find out? They are occupying an old world bunker. Well thats good to know I'll re-route some caraves to take different roads to avoid that area. Here is your payment."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_FORSAKENREJECTS_ITEMNAME"] = "Facility Outline"


