lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_BONETRENCHES"] = "The Bone Trenches"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_BONETRENCHES_DESC"] = "Nihao Banlu, I assume your interested in helping us scout some more points of interest. The first place I need you to investigate is a super mutant hotspot to the east of the refugee camp. Find out why there is such a high concentration of them in that area then return to me and you get the standard fee plus extra."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_BONETRENCHES_HINT"] = "Go to the Bone Trenches filled with Rejects outside of the Survivor Camp to the right clear it out and reach the center scout it then return to Mei-Lian."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_BONETRENCHES_COMPLETE"] = "I see you return triumphant, lets hear what you found. Nothing besides a bunker door and some fanatics? Well, I guess it is something atleast here is your payment."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_SHADOWRUIN"] = "Shadows in the Ruins"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_SHADOWRUIN_DESC"] = "Nihao Banlu, I have another target I need you to scout. This time its in the oposite side of the city. In our efforts to avoid the supermutants dotted around the city we altered our routes but we ran into a group of raiders wearing tanned leather. They decimated our caravan, I need you to go find out where they are coming from and mark it down. Same fee as always plus extra like last time."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_SHADOWRUIN_HINT"] = "Go to the Shadowed Fort filled with Shadowed Bandits outside the Survivor Camp to the left and straight down the road. Go into the fort and reach the top floor then return to Mei-Lian."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_SHADOWRUIN_COMPLETE"] = "You're back good, I hope you killed two of those raiders for everyone of our own. Tell me what you found and I'll pay you. They have a base to the east that they use an ambush point for travelers? Well that explains alot. Here is your payment."

--A potential quest that leads to the Energy Ammo crafting area that was planned to be added to Salem


-- General Tutorial Quest

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTURP"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Turpentine)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTURP_DESC"] = "Alright Outlander, I have a acquisition task for you. I need you to go find three turpentine for me. They are used in the process of tanning gecko hides a component in making a stronger iteration of leather armor."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTURP_HINT"] = "Collect 3 Turpentine and Return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTURP_COMPLETE"] = "You got the terpentine? Excellent, now follow me lets head to a campfire and I will show you how the leather tanning process works"

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINFIBER"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Ballistic Fiber)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINFIBER_DESC"] = "I have another acquisition task for you. I need you to go search for a couple stands of ballistic fiber located around old pre-war installations. Once you get the fibers I'll show you how to craft ballistic polymer."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINFIBER_HINT"] = "Collect 3 Ballistic Fiber and return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINFIBER_COMPLETE"] = "Alright let me see the fibers. These look pristine nice work, now lets head over to a work bench and I'll show how to craft the polymer"

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINPOLY"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Ballistic Polymer)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINPOLY_DESC"] = "Outlander now that I've shown you how to craft a ballistic polymer I need you to make one on your own. Collect the materials to craft the polymer then follow the process I showed you at the workbench. After that come back to me and I'll show you its uses."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINPOLY_HINT"] = "Collect 1 Ballistic Polymer and return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINPOLY_COMPLETE"] = "Welcome back, that took you a while. Anyway follow me to the armor bench and I'll show you the different uses for that polymere whether it be crafting combat armor of reinforcing your current armor with ballistic weave."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINADVMAT"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Advanced Materials)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINADVMAT_DESC"] = "You're quite a fast learner for a waster it is a nice change of pace but lets get back to it. I have a couple more tips for you there first is there is an item you need to keep an eye for. Its called an adavanced material it has a myriad of uses from weapon manufacturing to being a key component in making some of the biggest and baddest gear around. Find one and bring it to me once you do I'll show you some of the uses and pay you for it."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINADVMAT_HINT"] = "Collect 1 Advanced Materials and return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINADVMAT_COMPLETE"] = "You actually found one? Thats quite the surprise, anyway lets get you some payment for finding it just let me study its properties then I'll hand it back. Also you should be able to use these at a large array of work benches but the biggest application is making power armor."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINGOLD"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Gold Bar)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINGOLD_DESC"] = "I have a simple retrieval task for you Outlander. I need you to go find me two gold bars and return to me. Your payment will be keeping a majority of the gold on the bar I just need to a little bit to repair some electronics. Also you should be on the look out for them anyway quite a few groups will trade some rare goods for them."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINGOLD_HINT"] = "Collect 2 Gold Bar and return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINGOLD_COMPLETE"] = "You're back well funny thing is one of our guards find them for me before you got back. Keep the bars anyway and atleast you learned something while looking for it."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINSTAR"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Star Bottlecaps)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINSTAR_DESC"] = "Got another task for you Outlander I need you to find me something odd. We have a client operating our of Reno offering us quite the lucrative contract if we can provide proof of capital. Odd part is that capital he's talking about has nothing to do with caps or NCR dollars he wanted something called stars. I have no idea what that even means but based on my investigating apparently there is an underground market of hard to get goods being trafficed for some old caps with a special star imprinted on them. Find me 5 and I'll make it worth your while."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINSTAR_HINT"] = "Collect 1 Star Bottlecap and return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINSTAR_COMPLETE"] = "Thank the Emperor you got back in time. The client was starting to get wary of working with us let me see the cap and I'll be back. ... Thank you Outlander, you have helped more than you know here take the caps back as reward for your help."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTECH"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Tech Data)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTECH_DESC"] = "There you are Outlander! You really helped us out with those star caps! I have a personal request for you now though, I have some family back down south that requires some special information in order to help them work on a special project. If you would be kind enough to assist me in this task Banlu I would be in your debt all you need to do is find a set of 5 technical documents that can be used for research. You most likely wouldnt have any use for them but factions around the waste can make good use of that information."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTECH_HINT"] = "Collect 5 Technical Data and return to Mei Lian"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_TURNINTECH_COMPLETE"] = "Banlu you have retured did you find the documents? Wonderfull you once again have helped me more than you know. Let me copy the information down and you can keep the original documents. You can either sell them or hand them to a faction of your choice for their own research purposes."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOBREAK"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Breakdown Ammo)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOBREAK_DESC"] = "Before I let you head out of here and join us on a caravahn route I need to know you can take care of yourself. I have a simple task to test your aptitude. I just need you to break down some ammo at the local ammo press then return to me."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOBREAK_HINT"] = "Collect 25 9mm and break it down for its powder, lead, primers, and casings then return to Mei-Lian."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOBREAK_COMPLETE"] = "You got that done without blowing yourself up. You did better than the last waster that tried."

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOCRAFT"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Assemble Ammo)"
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOCRAFT_DESC"] = "Alright you can disassemble ammo but can you reverse the process and do it right. Go back to the ammo press with the materials you got from the breakdown and make some ammo you're going to use on the road. After that comeback to me and we can set out."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOCRAFT_HINT"] = "Collect the powder, lead, primers, and casings to craft 18 9mm and assemble them at a reloading bench then return to Mei-Lian."
lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_AMMOCRAFT_COMPLETE"] = "You made the bullets? Okay I want you to stand 12 feet away from me and fire. You didnt blow a hole in your neck good!"

lang["#MISSION_MEILIAN_PA"] = "Wasteland Wisdom (Titans of the Old World)"
